启动步骤：
docker启动frontend和nginx，本地启动Langgraph和gateway

步骤：
1.Docker 启 frontend nginx
docker compose -p deer-flow-dev -f docker-compose-dev.yaml up --build -d --no-deps frontend nginx
2.启动gateway-local
3.启动Langgraph-local
4.打开 http://localhost:2026

 $env:HOME = $env:USERPROFILE
 $env:GATEWAY_UPSTREAM = "host.docker.internal:8001"
 $env:LANGGRAPH_UPSTREAM = "host.docker.internal:8001"
 $env:LANGGRAPH_REWRITE = "/api/"

docker compose 启动：
docker compose -p deer-flow-dev -f docker-compose-dev.yaml up --build -d --no-deps frontend nginx

docker compose 结束：
docker compose -p deer-flow-dev -f docker-compose-dev.yaml down

验证nginx配置：
docker exec deer-flow-nginx sh -lc 'echo GATEWAY_UPSTREAM=$GATEWAY_UPSTREAM; echo LANGGRAPH_UPSTREAM=$LANGGRAPH_UPSTREAM; echo LANGGRAPH_REWRITE=$LANGGRAPH_REWRITE'

